OL,3,CInquest of Mum and four children
OL,4,Cmurdered in arson attack is delayed
OL,6,FA coroner has told the family of a
OL,7,Fmother and her four children who died
OL,8,Fin an arson attack that with "profound
OL,9,Fregret" he needs to delay an inquest
OL,10,Finto their deaths.
OL,12,FThe house blaze in Walkden, Greater
OL,13,FManchester, claimed the lives of Demi
OL,14,FPearson, 15, her brother Brandon,
OL,15,Feight, and sisters Lacie, seven, and
OL,16,FLia, three, in December 2017.
OL,18,FTheir mother, Michelle Pearson, 37,
OL,19,Fsuffered extensive burns injuries and
OL,20,F"clung on to life" until she died 20
OL,21,Fmonths later.
