OL,3,CInquest of Mum and four children
OL,4,Cmurdered in arson attack is delayed
OL,6,FHowever GMP has since notified the
OL,7,Fpolice watchdog of "some concerns"
OL,8,Fover the IOPC probe and asked it to
OL,9,Freview it.
OL,11,FAt a pre-inquest review hearing on
OL,12,FWednesday, Nicholas Flanagan,
OL,13,Frepresenting the IOPC, told Bolton
OL,14,FCoroner's Court that review is
OL,15,F"nearing its conclusion" with a
OL,16,Fdecision expected in the next
OL,17,Ffortnight as to whether a fresh
OL,18,Finvestigation is required.
OL,26,@oD@TOUoD@bO]wD@AOUwD@XO]
