OL,6,FHe said it is "far better" to hear the
OL,7,Fevidence all at one time rather than
OL,8,Fin a series of rolling part-heard
OL,9,Fsessions.
OL,11,FAnna Morris KC, representing the
OL,12,Ffamily, said: "It is of course their
OL,13,Fwish that the inquest takes place as
OL,14,Fsoon as possible given their long-
OL,15,Fstanding desire for the matters to be
OL,16,Fthoroughly investigated, but they are
OL,17,Fclear they want things done
OL,18,Fthoroughly."
