OL,3,CInquest of Mum and four children
OL,4,Cmurdered in arson attack is delayed
OL,6,FA further pre-inquest review,
OL,7,Fscheduled to last a full day, will
OL,8,Ftake place on June 16.
OL,10,FZak Bolland and David Worrall were
OL,11,Fjailed for life for the murders and
OL,12,Ftold they would serve a minimum of 40
OL,13,Fand 37 years respectively for the
OL,14,Fpetrol bomb attack on the Pearson
OL,15,Ffamily home in Jackson Street in the
OL,16,Fearly hours of December 11 2017.
OL,18,FBolland's girlfriend, Courtney
OL,19,FBrierley, was jailed for 21 years for
OL,20,Ffour counts of manslaughter after the
OL,21,Ftrial at Manchester Crown Crown Court.
